commit.message:
support other ext tasks except aso task and fix sentiment analysis based on SKEP (#4357)

1. support for common sentiment analysis functions: a, o, as, ao, aso, cls extraction, open up the whole process of each task from annotation description-data annotation-sample construction-model training-sentiment analysis visualization
2. For prompts with emotional elements such as sample construction, visual scripts, etc., fixed attributes, opinion words, and emotional tendencies, parameter customization is no longer provided, which lowers the threshold for users to understand and use
3. Optimize the labeling document, which is easy for users to understand, and add all supported labeling task descriptions
4. Optimize project operation log output
5. Upgrade the sentiment analysis based on SKEP to solve the word segmentation problem caused by tokenizer upgrade
